Sentencas: NdSrCo1-xFexO4+delta (0 <= x <= 1.0) intergrowth oxides have been investigated as cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Characterization of NdSrCo1-xFexO4+δ (0 ≤ x ≤ 1.0) intergrowth oxide cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: All the cathodes prepared by a glycine nitrate process (GNP) indicated single phase intergrowth oxides.
Titulo: Characterization of NdSrCo1-xFexO4+δ (0 ≤ x ≤ 1.0) intergrowth oxide cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The introduction of Fe for Co leads to decrease TEC values and electrical conductivity, and increase polarization resistance and oxygen content.
Titulo: Characterization of NdSrCo1-xFexO4+δ (0 ≤ x ≤ 1.0) intergrowth oxide cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The polarization resistance of NdSrCoO4+delta composition is 0.16 Omega cm(2) at 800 degrees C in air atmosphere, which is the best electrochemical performance compared with other compositions.
Titulo: Characterization of NdSrCo1-xFexO4+δ (0 ≤ x ≤ 1.0) intergrowth oxide cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
